All units are currently leased on a month-to-month basis, presenting a lucrative cash flow opportunity in the heart of West Palm Beach. Situated in close proximity to downtown West Palm Beach, the railway station, a supermarket, and top-rated schools, this property promises both convenience and substantial returns. Don't miss out on this money-making gem in West Palm Beach!
